## Command-Line Interface

```bash
# Extract lemma
marathi-shabda lemma ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§µ‡§∞

# Dictionary lookup
marathi-shabda lookup ‡§™‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä

# Full analysis
marathi-shabda analyze ‡§Æ‡•Å‡§≤‡§æ‡§®‡•á
```

